   text:'/ralph-loop "' + E + 'ЗАДАЧА: OAuth2 с PKCE (Authorization Code + PKCE).\n\nFLOW:\n1. Client: generate code_verifier (43-128 chars), code_challenge=SHA256(verifier).\n2. Authorize URL: response_type=code, code_challenge, state, scope.\n3. User login + consent.\n4. Callback: ?code=... → POST /token с code_verifier.\n5. Server: verify code_challenge == SHA256(code_verifier).\n6. Return access_token (15min JWT) + refresh_token (30d).\n\nPROVIDERS:\n- Google / GitHub / Microsoft / Apple / custom SSO.\n- discovery: /.well-known/openid-configuration.\n\nSECURITY:\n- state: anti-CSRF, привязка к session.\n- nonce: anti-replay.\n- HTTPS only.\n- redirect_uri whitelist (exact match).\n- Short-lived access_token, rotating refresh_token.' + A + '" --completion-promise "DONE"',
