   text:'/ralph-loop "' + E + 'ЗАДАЧА: JWT key rotation + refresh token strategy.\n\nKEYS:\n1. Generate RSA-2048 или Ed25519 keypair.\n2. JWKS endpoint: /.well-known/jwks.json (публичный ключ).\n3. Key ID (kid) в JWT header.\n4. Rotate: каждые 30-90 дней, grace period 2×TTL.\n5. Multiple active keys: old + new, verify пробует оба.\n\nTOKENS:\n- Access token: 15min, JWT.\n- Refresh token: 30d, opaque (random 32 bytes), в БД.\n- Rotation: каждый refresh → new refresh token (old invalid).\n- Reuse detection: old refresh использован → revoke whole family.\n\nREVOCATION:\n- Blacklist jti в Redis (TTL = token TTL).\n- Logout: delete refresh token + blacklist access.\n- Admin-initiated: revoke all sessions user_id.' + A + '" --completion-promise "DONE"',
